legacy.full_text: Speaking at the @USChinaBusiness Gala 2022. As the world’s top two economies, China and the US need & can cooperate in more & greater areas. None of us wants to see global warming, but all of us want to see a “warming” of China-US cooperation. Full speech: https://t.co/aIR7Ler0lf https://t.co/VMJdp17ctg

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text:
Congratulations to Zoey Cardamone (卡羽彤) from Minnesota for being crowned the world champion of #ChineseBridge competition!
Language is a great bridge. I encourage u and many others to go further down this bridge and get to know more about Chinese culture and friends! 加油！ https://t.co/wLJZZ1u8MJ

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: In early 2020, President Xi Jinping wrote back to kids from Cascade Elementary School who were learning Chinese and sent him Chinese New Year cards. It was a privilege for me to unveil President Xi’s original letter during my visit to Utah and meet with the kids. https://t.co/XVl4KOMaFo

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: I see great hope for better China-US relations in these students who are not only learning Chinese but also learning about China, as hundreds of millions of Chinese students are learning English and about USA in China. https://t.co/fTYzvoJNkH

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: Deeply touched by 1979 @BYU Young Ambassadors,1st art group to visit China since we established diplomatic relations. Like Randy said, no matter what’s happening in our world, ppl always remember the strong ties of love & friendship. Look forward to their next visit to China too! https://t.co/xD0seRanbg

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: I also thoroughly enjoyed the thrilling performance of the current BYU Young Ambassadors, and I wish their next tour to China another great success! https://t.co/va3eIlCC4O

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States

legacy.description: Pawn Man on TikTok and YouTube. Author of UBERED and Wolf in the Jungle.
legacy.name: Evan Kail (PAWN MAN)

legacy.full_text: Today I met with representatives from China and donated the World War 2 photo album. I want to thank China and all the people who stood by me throughout this process. It has been a life changing experience. https://t.co/IQJk76A0DU

Thank you Evan for donating the precious album of historic significance to the Chinese people. The atrocities by Japanese militarism should never be forgotten. Facts should not be denied, nor can they be denied. Let's remember history as a gateway to a better future.

legacy.full_text: 1. President Xi Jinping met with @UN Secretary-General  @antonioguterres. He pointed out that the world is undergoing momentous changes. Major countries need to set a good example and play a leading role so as to bring more confidence and strength to the world. https://t.co/htmg6FdS6k

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: 4. “China will strengthen cooperation with the @UN and jointly work for solid progress on the #GlobalDevelopmentInitiative and the #GlobalSecurityInitiative. China will continue to uphold true multilateralism and give firm support to the work of the UN.”

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: 5. “China will strive to promote the overall progress of mankind through Chinese modernization and create new opportunities for the world through its further development, with a view to adding more stability and certainty to a volatile world.”

legacy.full_text: 3. Follow an innovation-driven approach and facilitate post-pandemic recovery. China has proposed the #G20 Action Plan on Digital Innovation and Cooperation. We welcomes the participation of all parties.

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text:
“What is wrong with this world & what we should do about it？”Faced with the question of our times, China’s answer is that we should work together to meet the challenges and build a better future. Remarks by President Xi Jinping at #G20BaliSummit Session I
https://t.co/aBrxgjR4oq https://t.co/ZVikYIZSi8

1⃣"We should make global development more inclusive and elevate our win-win cooperation to a new height. We should make global development beneficial to all. Prosperity and stability cannot be possible in a world where the rich become richer while the poor are made poorer."

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: 5⃣"We must resolutely oppose the attempt to politicize food and energy issues or use them as tools and weapons. Unilateral sanctions must be removed, and restrictions on relevant scientific and technological cooperation must be lifted."

legacy.description: 11th Chinese Ambassador to the United States
legacy.name: Qin Gang 秦刚

legacy.full_text: 6⃣"A China marching toward modernization will bring more opportunities to the world, inject stronger momentum for international cooperation, and make greater contribution to human progress." #20thCPCNationalCongress
